txt.en: High above the Morgul Vale, in a cleft in the side of Achathras, lies Gath Daeroval, home to the Shadow-roost of the fell beasts. The Olag-hai here guard the roost, preventing any danger to the nest while the brood-mother hunts for food. Seek out and defeat these vile creatures.
Defeat Olag-hai within Gath Daeroval, the Shadow-roost.
